Berthe Emillene Etane Ngolle (amụrụ na ụbọsị 19 May 1995) bụ onye Cameroon na-agba mgba. Ọ bụ onye nwetara ọlaọcha ugboro abụọ na African Games
O meriri ihe nrite ọla edo na ihe omume ya na 2022 African Wrestling Championships nke emere na El Jadida, Morocco.
O sonyere na asọmpi ụmụ nwanyị nke 62 kilogram na 2018 Commonwealth Games na Gold Coast, Australia.
N'afọ 2019, ọ nọchitere anya Cameroon na African Games ma merie ọlaọcha na freestyle 62 kg nke ụmụ nwanyị.

N'afọ 2021, o sonyere na asọmpi African & Oceania Olympic Qualification Tournament na-atụ anya iru eru maka 2020 Summer Olympics na Tokyo, Japan. Ọ mechiri n'ọnọdụ nke atọ. Ọ nwetakwara ike iru eru maka Olimpik na World Olympic Qualification Tournament nke emere na Sofia, Bulgaria.
